{"tid":2272817,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"2020 入息統計  連登仔排頭11%  你的人工在全港排第幾？","createTime":"2020-11-05T09:54:48.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-06T06:38:56.000Z","uid":248054,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"77320873e261acf8069c4bcc1d607dc2265d8ebb","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T09:54:48.000Z","msg":"究竟你的人工算高還是低？相信是不少人一直的疑問。根據最新2020年統計處《政府統計年報》公布最新個人入息及家庭入息數字，現時全港個人入息中位數為17,000元，意味你月入17,000元，收入已經比全港一半人還要好。<br />\n<br />\n最新數據更顯示，與2014年相比，2019年年薪過百萬的「打工皇帝」人數更是大幅增加！以下即刻睇自己人工及家庭入息於全港排名。"},{"pid":"41b06d950548413a38b86717649ba9822261189e","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:00:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b07oZN7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb07oZN7.png&h=d61a3368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n100k: 2.73%<br />\n80k: 4.25%<br />\n60k: 7.59%"},{"pid":"2a16c8403db348d7bc7d62dc55305a95bc3a6f06","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4RDSS98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4RDSS98.jpg&h=dab2c9ed&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8jQ9Vot.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8jQ9Vot.png&h=6f331ed6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0291ab9af7a731b44ea07b78dce73317f854bb65","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:02:14.000Z","msg":"過去數年月薪5萬元以上的高薪一族人大幅增加，當中月入8萬或以上的「打工中產」，由2014年的92,600人，增加76.8%至19年的163,700人，同期香港打工仔總數只增加2.8%。"},{"pid":"4ebaae83dc334b45ce8542e219bd38b468fb1a06","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:02:51.000Z","msg":"假若你月入3萬元，薪金已比全港七成半打工仔還要高，而月入5萬元或以上者，人工比全港九成打工仔高，成為全港最高收入的一成人。<br />\n<br />\n@Wound RN"},{"pid":"d65dd41601dd70dec86835008142ced87b7790ad","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:03:02.000Z","msg":"若以家庭為單位計算，家庭總收入為35,500元，即意味家庭月入高於全港一半家庭。假設家庭總收入達50,000元，即排名全港最高收入的33%，比全港三分二家庭收入還要高。"},{"pid":"d661d07d7fa70e2406fc2d3bf29984267e76faed","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:03:38.000Z","msg":"根據最新稅務局年報顯示，2017/18年度政府薪俸稅收總額逾604億元，全港187萬名納稅人中，有3,011名年薪逾千萬的「打工皇帝」佔總納稅人0.16%，他們合共賺取684.7億元，人均年薪2,274.1萬元。不過，收入越高繳稅越多，一眾打工皇帝合共繳稅逾100億元，<span class=\"red\">人均繳稅334萬元，佔全港16.68%。</span>"},{"pid":"aafa6dcb47f0180ee3eab5878ba96e0764eada89","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:05:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OhGw8KO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOhGw8KO.jpg&h=52df68b4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aovU6wt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaovU6wt.jpg&h=76444397&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8b1fe122ecc92c9ac0b3bdd8667958fab0d26cc","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:17:54.000Z","msg":"香港真係好多高收入人士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f1af38c2692d370b594a91cab2d99adff761ad","tid":2272817,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31c83eb83036b2a006a7ecdd5a6210db4c317a0b","tid":2272817,"uid":248054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2f1af38c2692d370b594a91cab2d99adff761ad","tid":2272817,"uid":34525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T10:52:58.000Z","msg":"0<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T13:14:50.000Z","msg":"人生等於0<img src=\"/asse